data.description: WOW!!! OMG! Amazing, Stunning, Glenview home!! Rare to find!! Don't be fooled by appearances - this gem is larger than it looks! Spacious living awaits you  So much Luxury! The Perfect location! Move right into this beautifully updated home! 3 Huge bedrooms & 2 Gorgeous Bathrooms!! Open floor plan brings a great flow through the house! Beautiful updated kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances! Dining area connected to the living room. Huge yard and 3 car detached garage!! Home sits on Massive 61x170 ft lot!! This home has everything!! EXCELLENT location close to restaurants, golf course, shopping, airport & highway! You can't beat it! TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THIS, FEELS LIKE A BRAND NEW HOME!! COME AND SEE ALL THIS LUXURY! YOU'RE GOING TO LOVE IT!
